1574
02:03:16.261 --> 02:03:22.466
GRINDELWALD: <i>You have suffered
the most heinous of betrayals.</i>

1575
02:03:22.468 --> 02:03:25.068
most purposely
bestowed upon you

1576
02:03:25.070 --> 02:03:29.305
