1587
02:04:27.333 --> 02:04:29.035
Aurelius.

1588
02:04:30.235 --> 02:04:33.072
Aurelius Dumbledore.

1589
02:04:34.639 --> 02:04:36.640
We will go down
in history together

1590
02:04:36.642 --> 02:04:39.845
